OL,3,CBusiness owner calls for rates system
OL,4,Cto be scrapped
OL,6,FA small business owner in Strabane has
OL,7,Fcalled for the rates system in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland to be scrapped and
OL,9,Frevised.
OL,11,FLast week the Finance Minister John
OL,12,FO'Dowd hit the brakes on a revaluation
OL,13,Fof properties that saw some sectors
OL,14,Ffacing hikes to their bills.
OL,16,FNiall Speak from Eco Basket said:
OL,17,F"Rates are a massive, massive factor
OL,18,Fand why a lot of businesses here have
OL,19,Fclosed their shutters.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
