OL,3,CBusiness owner calls for rates system
OL,4,Cto be scrapped
OL,6,F"Longevity really needs to be given to
OL,7,Fa lot of businesses and the only way
OL,8,Fto actually do that is to scrap the
OL,9,Frates system and revise it and look at
OL,10,Fwhat can be done going forward,
OL,11,Fbecause it's really not for purpose
OL,12,Fand it is failing town center and
OL,13,Findependent businesses."
OL,15,FIt comes as representatives from the
OL,16,Fhospitality industry and the high
OL,17,Fstreet were questioned by MLAs on what
OL,18,Fneeds to happen next to find a long
OL,19,Fterm solution to the issue.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
