OL,3,CBusiness owner calls for rates system
OL,4,Cto be scrapped
OL,6,FColin Neill from Hospitality Ulster
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's a chicken and egg that
OL,8,Fwe've gone round in circles umpteen
OL,9,Ftimes on this, and I'm hoping now this
OL,10,Fwill allow us to break that circle.
OL,12,F"You know, we need to build it on
OL,13,Fevidence that people feel they'll get
OL,14,Fa fair hearing, that the model will
OL,15,Fgive them a fair outcome."
OL,17,FWith some large hotels looking at
OL,18,Fbills increasing by hundreds of
OL,19,Fthousands of pounds - there has been a
OL,20,Fcall now to change the formula to
OL,21,Fcalculate their bills.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
