OL,3,CBusiness owner calls for rates system
OL,4,Cto be scrapped
OL,6,FJanice Gault from the NI Hotel
OL,7,FFederation said: "Turnover has risen
OL,8,Fconsiderably for the majority of
OL,9,Fpeople, profit has not, and that has
OL,10,Fto be taken into consideration.
OL,12,F"So within the framework itself, the
OL,13,Fmethodology, the primary prima facie
OL,14,Fcases, it's based on the turnover
OL,15,Fmodel, but the mechanisms behind that
OL,16,Fwe would be very keen to look at."
OL,18,FWith help being put in place for
OL,19,Fhospitality and the high street in
OL,20,FEngland, industry bodies want more
OL,21,Fschemes to help put in place here.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
