OL,3,CBusiness owner calls for rates system
OL,4,Cto be scrapped
OL,6,FGlynn Roberts from Retail NI said: "Is
OL,7,Fthis a pause? Is this a one year
OL,8,Fsuspension? Will we be back at this in
OL,9,FJanuary next year? Where does this
OL,10,Fprocess fit in with the assembly
OL,11,Felection, which I know is all focusing
OL,12,Fvery heavily on all your minds, chair,
OL,13,Fso I think what we need is
OL,14,Fclarification."
OL,16,FJohn O'Dowd has said he is in
OL,17,Flistening mode and wants to find a
OL,18,Fsolution going forward - there has
OL,19,Fbeen plenty of talking in the last
OL,20,Ffortnight, it leaves a lot for him to
OL,21,Fconsider.
